Cost-Effectiveness of Craniotomy for Epidural Hematomas at a Major Government 
Hospital in Cambodia.

Moran D(1)(2), Shrime MG(3), Nang S(4), Vycheth I(4), Vuthy D(4), Hong R(4), 
Padula WV(2), Park KB(5)(6)(7).

Author information:
(1)Johns Hopkins University School of Medicine, 733 N Broadway, Baltimore, MD, 
21205, USA.
(2)Johns Hopkins Bloomberg School of Public Health, 615 N Wolfe St, Baltimore, 
MD, 21205, USA.
(3)Program in Global Surgery and Social Change, Department of Global Health and 
