Cost-effectiveness analysis of ultrasonography screening for nonalcoholic fatty 
liver disease in metabolic syndrome patients.

Phisalprapa P(1), Supakankunti S, Charatcharoenwitthaya P, Apisarnthanarak P, 
Charoensak A, Washirasaksiri C, Srivanichakorn W, Chaiyakunapruk N.

Author information:
(1)Faculty of Economics, Chulalongkorn University Division of Ambulatory 
Medicine Division of Gastroenterology, Department of Medicine Department of 
Radiology, Faculty of Medicine Siriraj Hospital, Mahidol University, Bangkok, 
Thailand School of Pharmacy, Monash University Malaysia, Selangor, Malaysia 
