Retinal vein occlusion and paroxysmal nocturnal hemoglobinuria.

Sorigue M(1), Juncà J(2), Orna E(2), Romanic N(3), Sarrate E(4), Castellvi J(3), 
Soler M(3), Rodríguez-Hernandez I(2), Feliu E(2), Ruiz S(3).

